data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ****PRICE REDUCTION 20k!!!!****Come experience the wonderful world of peace and tranquility!! Here you will find over a half acre of pure brilliance!! Check out this 3-4 bedroom 2 bath 4 car garage pool home!!!! This home is fully fenced in and offers exceptional privacy and seclusion which gives safety and a low traffic area.  Upon entering the home, you witness an open floor plan concept which includes a foyer, formal dining room, formal living/family room, office, two way entry kitchen, and breakfast nook. The master bedroom offers 2 walk in closets for that desired additional storage space along with a spacious master bathroom.  On the opposite end of the home, you will find the 2 additional bedrooms along with a large guest bathroom, and an office for work at home employees, and home school etc!!  Enjoy those holiday gatherings with friends and family with a full size screened in patio perfect for entertaining. But just in case you need to cool off, take a splash in a newly installed pool! But wait there’s more!! A new drain field installed 2020, and to the left of the home, there is an additional 2 car garage which is currently used as a workshop. In the rear of the workshop, there is an air conditioned bonus room which can be used as a 4th bedroom/private workshop!!  And top this, to sweeten the deal, the seller is leaving all appliances including the washer and dryer, and possibly a John Deere 0 turn mower! This home covers a large variety of your lifestyle needs and waiting for its new owners! Set up a showing today as this won’t last long!
